<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.5.9">
<l>pāloṭu neytayiroṇ cāntoṭu caṇpakamum</l>
<l rend="indent">paṅkayam nallakarup pūramum nāṟivara</l>
<l>kōlana ṟumpavaḷac centuvar vāyiṉiṭaik</l>
<l rend="indent">kōmaḷa veḷḷimuḷaip pōlcila pallilaka</l>
<l>nīlani ṟattaḻakā raimpaṭai yiṉṉaṭuvē</l>
<l rend="indent">niṉkaṉi vāyamuta miṟṟumu ṟintuviḻa</l>
<l>vēluma ṟaipporuḷē yāṭuka ceṅkīrai</l>
<l rend="indent">yēḻula kummuṭaiyā yāṭuka vāṭukavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>So that campaka with bright sandal, ghee and curds</l>
<l rend="indent">along with milk, and good camphor [with] lotus come emitting fragrance,</l>
<l>so that [your] few teeth like tender white shoots glisten</l>
<l rend="indent">between [your] red coral lips [like] beautiful and fragrant coral,</l>
<l>so that the nectar of your ripe mouth splits, breaks off and falls over</l>
<l rend="indent">in the midst of the beautiful five weapons [of you] with a blue colour,</l>
<l>O Meaning of the Vedas that are suitable, please dance!</l>
<l rend="indent">You who possesses the seven worlds, dance the Ceṅkīrai, please dance!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
